    <title>Creating High-Opportunity Neighborhoods: Evidence from the HOPE VI Program</title>
    <updated>2026-02-01T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Raj Chetty, Rebecca Diamond, Thomas B. Foster, Lawrence F. Katz, Sonya Porter, Matthew Staiger &amp; Laura Tach</name>
